Interface GUIDefaults

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdvancedConfigurationPage, ChangeFeatureDescriptionDialog, CircleDecoration, CollapsedDecoration, ConfigurationEditor, ConnectionEditPart, ConstraintDialog, ConstraintFigure, ConstraintProposalLabelProvider, DeleteOperationAlternativeDialog, ElementDeleteOperation, ExampleParent, FeatureCellEditorLocator, FeatureDiagramEditor, FeatureDiagramViewer, FeatureFigure, FeatureLabelEditManager, FeatureModelEditView, FeatureMoveEditPolicy, FeatureTreeDeleteOperation, FMLabelProvider, FMPropertyManager, FMPropertyPage, LegendFigure, LegendRelationDecoration, MoveElementsOperation, RelationDecoration, TwoColorGradientLine, ViewContentProvider, ViewLabelProvider

    public interface GUIDefaults
    Default colors, fonts, images and borders for the feature diagram.
    It is recommended to use FMPropertyManager for colors and borders instead of these values.
    Author:
    Thomas Thuem
